(1674, 547, 'sa_slide1_content', '<div class=\"prose\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<div class=\"testimonial-data-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"image-wrapper\">\r\n<span class=\"image\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/logo-in-slider-front-page.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-631\" />\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"title-rating-wrapper\">\r\n<span class=\"title h4\"><font style=\"font-family:Alata;font-size:18px\">Easy rental process, friendly staff</font></span>\r\n<br />\r\n<i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>We rented a ski boat a couple weeks ago. They didn\'t have the boat we wanted (it was already booked) but the boat we ended up with was just fine. The booking and renting process was super easy and the staff there were all friendly and helpful. The cost was very reasonable as well. I will definitely be renting with them again.</p>\r\n<cite> Eric R. | Facebook</cite>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>'),
