(1678, 547, 'sa_slide2_content', '<div class=\"prose\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<div class=\"testimonial-data-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"image-wrapper\">\r\n<span class=\"image\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/logo-in-slider-front-page.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-631\" />\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"title-rating-wrapper\">\r\n<span class=\"title h4\"><font style=\"font-family:Alata;font-size:18px\">We went there for the Memorial weekend.</font></span>\r\n<br />\r\n<i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>What an awesome place. Plenty of water, boats to rent are top notch, got steaks to bbq\'d on the boat(oh my!!!!) unbelievable tender and almost the same price as the market. Why bring food or drinks when they have it all right there!</p>\r\n<cite> Steve M. | Facebook</cite>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>'),
