(1682, 547, 'sa_slide3_content', '<div class=\"prose\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<div class=\"testimonial-data-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"image-wrapper\">\r\n<span class=\"image\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/logo-in-slider-front-page.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-631\" />\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"title-rating-wrapper\">\r\n<span class=\"title h4\"><font style=\"font-family:Alata;font-size:18px\">Great experience at the lake</font></span>\r\n<br />\r\n<i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i><i style=\'color:#f7bc51\' class=\'fa fa-star\'> </i>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>This was Danis last day of work at the Marina before she headed back to Chico. The owners, Darrin and Karin are always wanting people to have a great experience at the lake, even their employees! Lucky to live where we do Thank you Darrin and Karin.</p>\r\n<cite> Cindy R. | Facebook</cite>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>'),
