(1837, 584, 'sp_eap_upload_options', 'a:2:{s:18:\"eap_accordion_type\";s:17:\"content-accordion\";s:24:\"accordion_content_source\";a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:18:\"Do you allow pets?\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:178:\"Domestic pets are permitted aboard specific rental vessels. Pets must be leashed on the premises. There is an additional rental fee of $35.00 per pet (Maximum 2 pets per vessel).\";}i:1;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:62:\"Is there a special operating license required for boat rental?\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:193:\"No, for any vessel rental we only require the driver posses a valid drivers license. It is recommended that you check out California boating safety laws prior to your arrival at www.dbw.ca.gov.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:36:\"What is the age requirement to rent?\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:101:\"The minimum age is 25 years old to rent any vessel. Must present a valid drivers license at check-in.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:50:\"How far in advance do I need to make reservations?\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:191:\"To make sure you get the boat model and dates you want, reservations should be made as far in advance as possible. The summer months are increasingly popular, so booking early is recommended.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:42:\"What charges can be taken from my deposit?\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:113:\"Your deposit can be used pay for boat damage, loss of inventory, additional cleaning or late fees that you incur.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:42:\"Do we need any experience to drive a boat?\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:149:\"We have many first-time boaters. The captain and co-captain of the boat, as well as a few members of your party, will receive a hands-on orientation.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:68:\"Do you allow customers to store gasoline-filled containers on board?\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:169:\"No, for many safety reasons, we do not allow any sort of fuel to be stored on our houseboats or other rental vessels. Fuel is available for purchase at our Marina store.\";}}}'),
