(1863, 596, 'sp_eap_upload_options', 'a:2:{s:18:\"eap_accordion_type\";s:17:\"content-accordion\";s:24:\"accordion_content_source\";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:12:\"Boat Rentals\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:816:\"New Melones Lake Marina has many different options when it comes to our boat rentals. Dont worry if you dont have a boat yourself! No matter what you seek, we offer the boat for you. If you are planning on fishing, our 14 fishing boat is the boat you need. Dont forget to snag any fishing gear you may need from our convenience store. For a more relaxed cruise, check out our Patio Boats. They come equipped with a BBQ propane grill so you can grill up some delicious food while kicking back on the boat. We also offer larger deluxe cruisers that allow for all your friends and family to tag along and enjoy a day on the lake. On the opposite side of things, we also have sport boat rentals for those adrenaline seekers. These high-speed boats will have you smiling with your hair in the wind in no time.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:12:\"Slip Leasing\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:569:\"For those lucky ducks that already own a boat, you are going to want to check out the New Melones Lake Marina extended slip leasing. Our rates depend on availability. We offer annual or seasonal rates to suit you and your boating needs. Immerse yourself into the marina community while also having your own private slip to enjoy. Houseboat slips come with power hook-ups and in-dock servicing for added convenience. The New Melones Lake Marina slips are just a quick walk away from the main marina, allowing you to fully enjoy all the pleasures the marina has to offer.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:17:\"Water Toy Rentals\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:577:\"What better way to add to your already amazing vacation then to check out one of our water toy rentals. Walk-in rentals are available but are on a first come first served basis. So if you have a toy in mind you must rent, call ahead to ensure you have it for the time you want! You can rent on an hourly basis, daily or even weekly. Try one or more of the following for an exciting adventure:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Wake Surf Board</li>\r\n 	<li>Tubes</li>\r\n 	<li>Kneeboard</li>\r\n 	<li>Water Skis</li>\r\n 	<li>Jet Skis</li>\r\n 	<li>Kayaks</li>\r\n 	<li>SUPS</li>\r\n 	<li>And More!</li>\r\n</ul>\";}i:3;a:2:{s:23:\"accordion_content_title\";s:17:\"Houseboat Rentals\";s:29:\"accordion_content_description\";s:984:\"Renting a houseboat will give you the option to not only spend time on the lake but to have a place for you to sleep as well. If you are able to enjoy spending the night at New Melones Lake Marina, we have several houseboat rentals for you to choose from. All houseboats come equipped with a kitchen that includes a fridge, oven, and stove, plus a bathroom and sleeping quarters. Dont forget to bring your grillable foods to grill on the BBQ propane grill provided. Most of our houseboats also have a slide! Depending on the houseboat you choose, they can sleep anywhere from 8-16 people. Renting a houseboat is the way to go for your extended stay at New Melones Lake Marina. You can rent on a daily basis or we have three different houseboat packages for you to choose from:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>3 Night Stay  Friday afternoon to Monday morning</li>\r\n 	<li>4 Night Stay  Monday afternoon to Friday morning</li>\r\n 	<li>7 Night Stay  Monday afternoon to Monday morning</li>\r\n</ul>\";}}}'),
