(444, 1, '2022-03-25 23:33:59', '2022-03-25 23:33:59', '<div class=\"quick-details-box\">\r\n<h4 class=\"quick-details-header\">QUICK DETAILS</h4>\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-users\"></i> <strong>Passenger Capacity:</strong> Up to 4 passengers\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-paw\"></i> <strong>Pets Allowed:</strong> Yes\r\n\r\n<strong>Departure:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>9 a.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Return:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Daily 5 p.m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sunset 7 p.m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Overnight 8 a.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Note:</strong> Refundable security deposit is taken on the day of rental  $200\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Perfect for a day of fishing!</h2>\r\nRental boats may be picked up starting at 9 a.m. on the day of your rental. Overnight rentals are due back by 8 a.m. on your return day.\r\n\r\nOur four-passenger, 15-horsepower fishing boats will take you into all the nooks and crannies around the lake where youre sure to catch the big one.\r\n<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Things You Should Know</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>To rent a boat, you must be 25 YEARS OR OLDER and sign a rental agreement with valid Identification. All drivers must be 25 YEARS OR OLDER and present valid drivers license at check-in.</li>\r\n 	<li>Renting for a week constitutes 6 nights and 7 days. The rental must be returned by 5 p.m. on the 7th day.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rental hours during the summer season are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Monday  Sunday 9 a.m.  5 p.m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sunset and Overnight Return add-ons may be available and vary by rental.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Walk-in rentals are on a first-come, first-serve basis.</li>\r\n 	<li>There is a 2-hour minimum on all rentals  Hourly rentals CANNOT be reserved in advance.</li>\r\n 	<li>When paying the daily rate, your rental will be held all day, no matter what time you arrive. You WILL NOT lose your rental if you do not arrive at the scheduled beginning rental time. THE RENTAL IS DUE BACK AT 5PM.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />', '14 FISHING BOAT RENTAL', ' Passenger Capacity: Maximum 4<br>\r\n Bring your fishing poles.<br>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '308-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-03-25 23:33:59', '2022-03-25 23:33:59', '', 308, 'http://localhost/wordpress2/?p=444', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
