(632, 1, '2022-03-29 16:57:13', '2022-03-29 16:57:13', '<div class=\"grid grid-fify-fifty-columns\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h1>About Us</h1>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #2f7bbb;\">If you are looking for the perfect getaway, you have come to the right place!</h2>\r\nNew Melones Lake Marina has so much to offer you to help make those memories with all your friends and family. With all of our <a href=\"/wordpress2/sportboat-rentals\">boat rental</a> options, you don\'t have to worry about having a boat of your own to enjoy a day on the lake. When looking for a longer stay on the water, check out our houseboat rentals. The houseboats come equipped with kitchens, bathrooms and have a BBQ grill for you to use. Don\'t forget about our water toy rentals as well. These are great additions for your day on the lake.\r\n\r\nBe sure to chat up our friendly and knowledgeable staff about all the local attractions you can check out while you are here. Or visit our calendar page to see the upcoming events you won\'t want to miss out on! We also offer camping and lodging for you so you won\'t have to travel far to be able to keep enjoying your time at the lake. Combine all of these amazing options, and you\'ve got yourself a party. We have some of the best party packages for employee and customer appreciation, birthday parties and even wedding events. New Melones Lake Marina is really a one-stop-have-it-all vacationing spot! For a more long term stay, we provide extended slip leasing for the true boat enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nScope out our gallery to see what you are looking forward to by visiting New Melones Lake Marina. If you have any questions, you can see if your specific question is listed on our FAQ page. However, please don\'t hesitate to contact us with any and all questions you may have to ensure you make the most out of your stay at New Melones Lake Marina.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[gallery ids=\"368,375,213,579,580,581,281,582,502,258,500,293\"]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit