(658, 1, '2022-03-29 18:15:54', '2022-03-29 18:15:54', '<div class=\"grid grid-fify-fifty-columns\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h1>About Us</h1>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #2f7bbb;\">If you are looking for the perfect getaway, you have come to the right place!</h2>\r\nNew Melones Lake Marina has so much to offer you to help make those memories with all your friends and family. With all of our <a href=\"/sportboat-rentals\">boat rental</a> options, you don\'t have to worry about having a boat of your own to enjoy a day on the lake. When looking for a longer stay on the water, check out our <a href=\"/houseboat-rentals\">houseboat rentals</a>. The houseboats come equipped with kitchens, bathrooms and have a BBQ grill for you to use. Don\'t forget about our <a href=\"/watersport-rentals\">water toy rentals</a> as well. These are great additions for your day on the lake.\r\n\r\nBe sure to chat up our friendly and knowledgeable staff about all the <a href=\"/attractions\">local attractions</a> you can check out while you are here. Or visit our calendar page to see the upcoming events you won\'t want to miss out on! We also offer <a href=\"/rv-camping\">camping and lodging</a> for you so you won\'t have to travel far to be able to keep enjoying your time at the lake. Combine all of these amazing options, and you\'ve got yourself a party. We have some of the best <a href=\"/plan-your-party\">party packages</a> for employee and customer appreciation, birthday parties and even wedding events. New Melones Lake Marina is really a one-stop-have-it-all vacationing spot! For a more long term stay, we provide <a href=\"/slip-leasing\">extended slip leasing</a> for the true boat enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nScope out our <a href=\"/gallery\">gallery</a> to see what you are looking forward to by visiting New Melones Lake Marina. If you have any questions, you can see if your specific question is listed on our <a href=\"/faq\">FAQ page</a>. However, please don\'t hesitate to <a href=\"/contact-us\">contact us</a> with any and all questions you may have to ensure you make the most out of your stay at New Melones Lake Marina.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[gallery ids=\"368,375,213,579,580,581,281,582,502,258,500,293\"]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'tablet-or-mobile-display-only\'>\r\n[slide-anything id=\"655\"]\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-03-29 18:15:54', '2022-03-29 18:15:54', '', 11, 'http://localhost/wordpress2/?p=658', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
