(703, 1, '2022-03-30 23:06:04', '2022-03-30 23:06:04', '<div class=\"grid grid-fify-fifty-columns\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h1>About Us</h1>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #2f7bbb;\">If you are looking for the perfect getaway, you have come to the right place!</h2>\r\nNew Melones Lake Marina has so much to offer you to help make those memories with all your friends and family. With all of our <a href=\"/sportboat-rentals\">boat rental</a> options, you don\'t have to worry about having a boat of your own to enjoy a day on the lake. When looking for a longer stay on the water, check out our <a href=\"/houseboat-rentals\">houseboat rentals</a>. The houseboats come equipped with kitchens, bathrooms and have a BBQ grill for you to use. Don\'t forget about our <a href=\"/watersport-rentals\">water toy rentals</a> as well. These are great additions for your day on the lake.\r\n\r\nBe sure to chat up our friendly and knowledgeable staff about all the <a href=\"/attractions\">local attractions</a> you can check out while you are here. Or visit our calendar page to see the upcoming events you won\'t want to miss out on! We also offer <a href=\"/rv-camping\">camping and lodging</a> for you so you won\'t have to travel far to be able to keep enjoying your time at the lake. Combine all of these amazing options, and you\'ve got yourself a party. We have some of the best <a href=\"/plan-your-party\">party packages</a> for employee and customer appreciation, birthday parties and even wedding events. New Melones Lake Marina is really a one-stop-have-it-all vacationing spot! For a more long term stay, we provide <a href=\"/slip-leasing\">extended slip leasing</a> for the true boat enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nScope out our <a href=\"/gallery\">gallery</a> to see what you are looking forward to by visiting New Melones Lake Marina. If you have any questions, you can see if your specific question is listed on our <a href=\"/faq\">FAQ page</a>. However, please don\'t hesitate to <a href=\"/contact-us\">contact us</a> with any and all questions you may have to ensure you make the most out of your stay at New Melones Lake Marina.\r\n\r\n</div >\r\n<div class=\'about-us-gallery\'>\r\n[gallery link=\"none\" ids=\"368,375,213,579,580,581,281,582,502,258,500,293\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\'about-us-slider\'>\r\n[slide-anything id=\"655\"]\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-03-30 23:06:04', '2022-03-30 23:06:04', '', 11, 'https://newmeloneslakemarina.com/?p=703', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(706, 1, '2022-03-31 14:08:00', '2022-03-31 14:08:00', '<div class=\"quick-details-box\">\r\n<h4 class=\"quick-details-header\">QUICK DETAILS</h4>\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-users\"></i> <strong>Passenger Capacity:</strong> Up to 26 passengers\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-paw\"></i> <strong>Pets Allowed:</strong> Yes\r\n\r\n<strong>Departure:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>9 a.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Return:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Daily 5 p.m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Overnight 8 a.m. + $250</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Note:</strong> Refundable security deposit is taken on the day of rental  $1,000\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Our 60 Party Cruiser is perfect for up to 26 passengers!</h2>\r\nThe Party Cruiser holds up to 26 passengers and is equipped with a bathroom, shower, barbecue, side-by-side kitchen sink, 4-burner stovetop, stereo, slide, sun deck, plenty of storage, lounge chairs and plenty of seating.\r\n\r\nRental boats may be picked up starting at 9 a.m. on the day of your rental. Overnight rentals are due back by 8 a.m. on your return day.\r\n<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Things You Should Know</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>To rent a boat, you must be 25 YEARS OR OLDER and sign a rental agreement with valid Identification. All drivers must be 25 YEARS OR OLDER and present valid drivers license at check-in.</li>\r\n 	<li>Renting for a week constitutes 6 nights and 7 days. The rental must be returned by 5 p.m. on the 7th day.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rental hours during the summer season are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Monday  Sunday 9 a.m.  5 p.m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sunset and Overnight Return add-ons may be available and vary by rental.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Walk-in rentals are on a first-come, first-serve basis.</li>\r\n 	<li>There is a 2-hour minimum on all rentals  Hourly rentals CANNOT be reserved in advance.</li>\r\n 	<li>When paying the daily rate, your rental will be held all day, no matter what time you arrive. You WILL NOT lose your rental if you do not arrive at the scheduled beginning rental time. THE RENTAL IS DUE BACK AT 5PM.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<a class=\'post-pdf-link\' target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://newmeloneslakemarina.com/wp-content/uploads/pdfs/60_-PARTY-CRUISER\" rel=\"noopener\">Click to view Floorplan</a>', '60 PARTY CRUISER BOAT RENTAL', ' Passenger Capacity: Maximum 26<br>\r\n BBQ<br>\r\n Bathroom\r\n Kitchen<br>\r\n Shower<br>\r\n Slide<br>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '193-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-03-31 14:08:00', '2022-03-31 14:08:00', '', 193, 'https://newmeloneslakemarina.com/?p=706', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
